title: FABLES 135 (2014) (DC Vertigo) (Digital) (Nahga-Empire)
description:
A new era is beginning for the Farm as knights begin to arrive from every corner of countless worlds.

In the old version of Camelot, the brief shining moment was destroyed by infidelity, infighting and the evil machinations of the king's sister.

If Rose Red is the king this time, does that mean Snow White is the one destined to bring it all crashing down around them?

Written by: Bill Willingham
Art by: Mark Buckingham, Russell Braun
Cover by: Greg Ruth

Color, 32 Pages
U.S. Price: 2.99
On Sale: November 20, 2013
